comments: Siakam (TOR) has his hand rested on Vanderbilt's (MIN) back and marginal contact occurs as Siakam releases away to back-tap the ball.
Vanderbilt (MIN) makes contact across Powell's (TOR) left arm and causes him to lose control of the ball after his gather.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Bembry's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.
Rubio (MIN) brings his off-arm toward Bembry's (TOR) side and marginal contact occurs as Rubio changes direction.
Siakam (TOR) rests his forearm on Towns' (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs as Towns is passing.

As Lowry (TOR) and Vanderbilt (MIN) attempt to establish position in the lane, marginal contact occurs between the two players.  Vanderbilt's momentum carries him towards the boundary line as he goes to catch the pass.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Vanderbilt (MIN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Towns (MIN) is moving laterally as body contact occurs with Lowry (TOR) after his gather.

Bembry (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Rubio's (MIN) path and absorbs the side-to-side contact.
Towns (MIN) establishes a legal guarding position in Lowry's (TOR) path and absorbs the body contact made along the perimeter.

Towns (MIN) is moving laterally and not established in a legal guarding position at the time of the contact with Bembry (TOR) during his driving shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) reaches in and makes contact across Edwards' (MIN) left arm, causing him to lose control of the ball.
Bembry (TOR) jumps alongside Beasley (MIN) and brushes Beasley's side as marginal contact occurs.
VanVleet (TOR) swipes forward and cleanly dislodges the ball from Beasley (MIN) before incidental contact occurs.
Edwards (MIN) and Bembry (TOR) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Beasley (MIN) steps out of bounds with his right foot.
McDaniels (MIN) moves alongside Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs after Siakam's gather.

Lowry (TOR) commits a take foul on McLaughlin (MIN).
Edwards (MIN) and Siakam (TOR) engage and disengage with one another as the inbound pass is made.
